18.08.2014 GB SCR18908 Added extended tests (see ODC711-changes13.doc to get more details)
R - Request limit for selected debtor
T - Request limit for selected debtor (no row selected and it is an existing debtor)
-- There is used the success indication
-- there is no debtor selected and it is a new debtor

Text.valUnicode: Please select the right debtor in table above, by clicking the checkbox in the first column. If the debtor you are looking for is not listed, you can create one yourself (button "manual debtor entry"), but no automatic decision will be possible. We will then process your limit request manually.

SQL_STMT_U.val: select count(*) from :1/EHR1 where EHR1_REQID = :2 and EHR1_EULERID<>0
